d-[50%] bg-[#e9ecef] hover:text-[var(--primary)]\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" title=\"B&aacute;o lỗi\" aria-label=\"Button\"><i class=\"icon inline-block font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-comment-exclamation1\"></i></button></span>\n  </div>\n </div>\n</div>"
